Gg_lost_temple

This is a medium sized map that is open in the middle.  There are four “temple” structures that line the outside of the map and all face inward.  Each team spawns on opposite sides of the map, and everything is symmetrical.  Buy Zones have been included just so people can play the map FY style if they wish.

-	44 Spawns, 22 per a team
-	Nav file for bots
-	Overview radar map
-	Cube Maps
-	3d Skybox
-       Buy Zones
-	Optimized with No Draw for better FPS
-	Everything is packaged into the .bsp with Pakrat

You can find the AWP version of this map here: http://www.fpsbanana.com/maps/112281

Blair (Bobpoblo) Burkhardt - Level Design
http://www.fpsbanana.com/members/776402
